Ing '''galumbang''' (''Jatropha curcas'' L.) metung yang species ning [[tanaman a manyampaga]] king familiang [[Euphorbia|spurge]], [[Euphorbiaceae]], a katutubu kareng lugal a tropical o mapali king [[Pangulung America]], malyaring [[Mexico]] ampong [[Kalibudtang America]].<ref name="Janick">{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=cjHCoMQNkcgC |first=Jules |last=Janick |coauthor=Robert E. Paull |title=The Encyclopedia of Fruit & Nuts |publisher=CABI |year=2008 |isbn=978-0-85199-638-7 |pages=371–372}}</ref> Tatanam de kareng labwad a  tropical ampong [[Subtropics|subtropical]] king mabilug a yatu, at darakal ne anti kareng tanamang katutubu kareng aliwang lugal. Minuna neng ing lagyu ning species,  ing ''"curcas"'', ning [[Portugal|Portugues]] a doktor, i [[Garcia de Orta]], maygit nang 400 (apat a ralan) a banwa ing milabas, at e siguradu nung nukarin ya ibat.<ref name="Agroforest">{{cite web |url=http://www.worldagroforestry.org/af/treedb/AFTPDFS/Jatropha_curcas.pdf |format=PDF |title='''Jatropha curcas''' L. Euphorbiaceae |work=Agroforestree Database 4.0 |publisher=World Agroforestry Centre |year=2009 |accessdate=2010-10-14}}</ref> Kayabe la kareng lagyu nang karaniwan king Ingles deng ''Barbados Nut'', ''Purging Nut'', ''Physic Nut'', o ''JCL'' (pamikuyad ning ''Jatropha curcas'' [[Carl Linnaeus|Linnaeus]]).

Ing galumbang metung yang makalasun a [[palungpung]] o malating [[pun dutung]], a miraras king kátas a 6 m (20 pie){{convert|6|m|ft|abbr=on}}.<ref name="Janick"/>  Agyu na ing malanging klima, anya mabibie ya kareng [[desiertu]].<ref>[http://www.ecoworld.com/home/articles2.cfm?tid=367 JATROPHA IN AFRICA. FIGHTING THE DESERT & CREATING WEALTH]</ref><ref>[http://www.new-ag.info/07/03/focuson/focuson3.php Jatropha: creating desert solutions]</ref> 

Atin lang 27-40% [[Vegetable fats and oils|laru]]<ref>Achten WMJ, Mathijs E, Verchot L, Singh VP, Aerts R, Muys B 2007. Jatropha biodiesel fueling sustainability?. Biofuels, Bioproducts and Biorefining 1(4), 283-291.[http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/bbb.39 <!-- Bot generated title -->] {{doi|10.1002/bbb.39}}[https://perswww.kuleuven.be/~u0053809/Index.html   The Jatropha Archives<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> (average: 34.4% <ref>Achten WMJ, Verchot L, Franken YJ, Mathijs E, Singh VP, Aerts R, Muys B 2008. Jatropha bio-diesel production and use. (a literature review) Biomass and Bioenergy 32(12), 1063-1084.[http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.biombioe.2008.03.003 <!-- Bot generated title -->] {{doi|10.1016/j.biombioe.2008.03.003}}[https://perswww.kuleuven.be/~u0053809/Index.html   The Jatropha Archives<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>) deng butul o biní a malyaring iprosesu bang gawang matas a uring panangab o ''fuel'' a [[biodiesel]], a malyaring gamitan king karaniwan a   [[makinang diesel]]. Atin la muring misnang mákalasun a [[toxalbumin]], ing curcin, deng butul.<ref>http://www.drugsandpoisons.com/2008/01/lectins-peas-and-beans-gone-bad.html</ref>

